    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Communication form which takes place through images, objects, gestures and/or colors. Examples of visual communication forms may include video or photographs, graphs, diagrams, infographics or other forms of data visualization, typography, maps, illustrations and graphic design, etc.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
